node.text:
Getting an idea of just how strong these LEDs from @floraflex really are!  My first time playing with @apogee_instruments and measuring out the ppfd within the canopy- 
Our goal here is to cultivate these ladies within with I like to call the *Goldilocks Zone* 

Anything too far away that isn’t getting appropriately illuminated should be removed early in the growth stage -

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Michelle 💙 Rad Reefer on July 19, 2021 tagging @frenchycannoli, and @madame_cannoli. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text:
💔💔💔There are no word to reflect how much you meant and inspired so many people. You taught me so many things, shared many stories.. 

It’s been a few seasons since I last laughed and smoked with you, I was honored to spend an hour with you on Herb TV over quarantine to catch up and share our passion. Tell me about your book and more life stories. 

when I first released my Fluer De Lis canna leaf logo over half a decade ago, you pulled me aside and reiterated the standard and quality I must uphold to rock the sacred symbol, and I took that very seriously and will continue to honor that promise throughout my life’s work. I am so sad by the news and all my love to my family and friends who are also feeling the loss of this very tidal wave of a man and movement and passion - all my love @madame_cannoli rest in paradise @frenchycannoli

node.text:
Pay little attention to what everyone else is achieving, this is a dance between who you were a year ago, and who you are today- you feel like you wasted so much time doing _______ … 

So here’s a little perspective shift.. stop managing your “time” and manage your focus. Focus on the little steps that you can take today. One day at a time darling. 💋 

Ps - yes.. these @floraflex lights are not only phenomenal .. but affordable.. and now shipping!

Sharing a little mid stretch trellis dance - while it’s always recommended to get your nets up all early and shit. It doesn’t always happen in a timely fashion and some things fall behind- 

I was struggling w low humidity in my dry climate [shout out to my @pulsegrow meter for keeping A close eye out on my VPD for me!!!]

so after ADDING a humidifier (I’ve always de-hu’d but it’s been so hot.. always something right??) and these ladies took offff 

🚀🚀🚀prepping to rock the  @floraflex trifecta here - w their newest Mid flower peak potassium shin dig- that BULKY B baby!!!! 

I’ll have to add extensions to the amazing @nextg3ngreenhouse rolling benches trellis poles and another net layer or two to the right table, she’s gonna be a leggy one lol

node.text: Some y’all know, most y’all don’t- I been goin thru some things and I just want to remind you that it’s ok to have the off days, the harder than most days - life is beautiful but it is also really fucking ugly- so be kind you know, never really know who’s goin thru it 🖤
